  "description": "A natural blackjack in [blackjack](../_index.md) is a two-card total of 21 made from an ace and any ten-value card [@shackleford2025blackjackcalculator]. It is structurally distinct from reaching 21 with three or more cards because casino rules usually pay it at a premium rather than at even money.",
